sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Dialog, DialogTitle, DialogContent, DialogActions, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material'; const ExamDetailsModal = ({ open, onClose, examName, examDuration, questionPicking, topics, negativeMarking, marks, passingScore, showRegistrationForm, captureImage, captureInterval, instructions, }) => { return ( Exam Details Exam Name: {examName} Exam Duration: {examDuration} minutes Question Picking: {questionPicking} Topics: {JSON.stringify(topics)} Negative Marking (%): {negativeMarking} Marks: Easy: {marks.easy}, Medium: {marks.medium}, Hard: {marks.hard} Minimum Passing Score (%): {passingScore} Show Registration Form: {showRegistrationForm ? 'Yes' : 'No'} Capture Image: {captureImage ? 'Yes' : 'No'} {captureImage && ( Capture Interval (seconds): {captureInterval} )} Instructions: {instructions} ); }; export default ExamDetailsModal;
